<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>교환 요청 응답 폼</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.socket.io/4.0.0/socket.io.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/socket.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
<h1>{{requesterNickname}}님이{{uploaderItem}}을(를) 교환 요청했습니다 </h1>

<p>요청자가 제시한 교환 물품: {{exchangeItem}}</p>
<p>교환 요청 메시지: {{exchangeRequest.message}}</p>

<!-- 응답 버튼 -->
<form action="/respondToExchangeRequest" method="post">
    <input type="hidden" name="requestId" value="{{exchangeRequest.id}}">
    <button type="submit" name="accept" value="true">교환 수락</button>
    <button type="submit" name="accept" value="false">교환 거절</button>
</form>

<form id="transactionStatusForm" style="display: none;">
    <h2>거래 상태 선택</h2>
    <button onclick="updateTransactionStatus(transactionId, true)">거래 완료</button>
    <button onclick="updateTransactionStatus(transactionId, false)">거래 미완료</button>
</form>

<div id="chatWindow" style="display: none;">
    <h2>채팅창</h2>
    <div id="messages"></div>
    <input id="messageInput" type="text" placeholder="메시지 입력">
    <button onclick="sendMessage()">메시지 보내기</button>
</div>
</body>
</html>